Titolo: The Legend of Sword and Fairy 4

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: The Legend of Sword and Fairy 4 is an action role-playing game developed by Softstar Technology (Shanghai) Co., Ltd.. It is the fifth installment in The Legend of Sword and Fairy (or Chinese Paladin) video game series, and serves as a prequel to the third game. The game incorporates elements of wuxia, shenmo and fantasy.